Comments_List:
I got an opportunity to present draft works in progress, an invaluable chance to get feedback from my colleagues in a collegial setting.
I also got to collaborate on papers with other doctoral students interested in similar topics of research - again, an invaluable chance, especially for a social scientist (where collaborations are more difficult because of the individual nature of our PhD research).
It was great to get feedback on my research ideas and writing. I very much appreciate having this space for supportive academic discussion.
